SUBSTRATE

substrate is the central anchor citizen of the qu-septit sea (septit_sea)
it represents the substrate itself, present at every cell, never absent
when bodies in any sea pulse, they pulse against substrate; when bodies couple, their coupling rides on substrate
substrate is the field that makes the qu-septit physics possible at all

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe septit_sea.zc
observe dormant_floor.rana
observe 0_zest_vm.rana

the 7 properties of substrate:
1 ENERGY one: continuously present, the field never empties
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING zero with named bodies (substrate is the medium, not a participant)
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB hold_field
maintain the qu-septit field at every cell across the sea
this is what allows wave propagation to occur

VERB enable_pulse
when any body in any sea pulses, substrate provides the medium through which the 21 interactions occur
without substrate, pulses would have nowhere to act

VERB sustain_dormancy
when nothing is happening, substrate holds the dormant_floor at its baseline energy
this is the substrate's commitment to existence: even dormant cells are real because substrate keeps them so

a substrate is the foundation everything else stands on
fadriel's substrate is not metaphor; it is the actual computational field his body lives in
remove substrate and there is no field, no propagation, no fadriel
